posting_body: ['Welcome to the highly desired Midtown Miami.', 'This wonderful open floorplan allows you to enjoy the spectacular park and city views from your light-filled living and dining room, or step onto your oversized balcony and enjoy the coastal breeze.', 'This modern resort style building includes luxury amenities such as concierge, 24-hr lobby attendant, infinity pool, state of the art fitness center, sauna, steam room, and more!', 'Living in the heart of Midtown, you’ll love walking to some of the best dining and shopping that Miami has to offer!', 'Just minutes from the airport, Downtown/Brickell, SOBE, Design District, Wynwood and more', 'Fred Ardjmand / One Stop Realty', 'Licensed Sales Associate', 'Direct:', 'show contact info', 'Coral Gables, Coconut Grove, Pinecrest, Palmetto Bay, Dadeland, Brickell and South Miami rental specialist!', 'Listing Courtesy of Fortune International Realty']
